Just created a new project and added the wiki.  The default Home.wiki file gave the wrong URL for the wiki repository (luckily noticed that there was another location where it was listed correctly.

Incorrect instructions included in the Home.wiki file:

{{{\\
$ hg clone http://bitbucket.org/clstopher/projectwiki/\\
}}}

Corrected instructions:

{{{\\
$ hg clone http://bitbucket.org/clstopher/project/wiki/\\
}}}

Note the "/" between "project" and "wiki".

when I try to qclone my patch repository with HTTPS, I always get\\
{{{\\
#!shell\\
$ hg qclone https://felixschwarz@bitbucket.org/felixschwarz/trac-l10n-de\\
requesting all changes\\
